# {{.ID}}

{{.Description}}

Pilot Protocol app-store adapter, generated by `pilot-app` from `pilot.app.yaml`.
It is a thin, stateless bridge: the daemon spawns it, it serves the app-store
IPC protocol on a unix socket, and forwards each method to the
{{.Backend.Type}} backend{{if eq .Backend.Type "http"}} at `{{.Backend.BaseURL}}`{{end}}.

